parameters.name: Seconds
parameters.description: Seconds of livetime in minute

parameters.name: MET_SEC
parameters.description: MET at mid-point of minute

parameters.name: Mission_Day
parameters.description: Mission day of level 0 files for this data point

parameters.name: Position
parameters.description: Spacecraft Position (GEO)

parameters.name: Position_Quality
parameters.description: Position quality flag: 0 - definitive, 1 - predicted

parameters.name: Orbit_Number
parameters.description: Orbit number

parameters.name: Orbit_Status
parameters.description: Orbit status: 0 = outbound, 1 = inbound

parameters.name: Orbit_Epoch
parameters.description: Decimal hours since perigee

parameters.name: EarthConeAngle
parameters.description: Half-angle of Earth as seen from Spacecraft

parameters.name: B_Meas
parameters.description: Measured magnetic field vector in GEO

parameters.name: B_Meas_Flag
parameters.description: Source of Measured field - 0 indicates MAG L0 file, 1 indicates MAG L1 file, etc. If 255, then the OPQ77 model field is used for computing Alpha and Beta

parameters.name: SPIN_OMEGA
parameters.description: RPS spin axis vector in GEO vector norm is spin rate

parameters.name: DATA_CHANNEL_COUNTS
parameters.description: Counts in data channels based on EVENT_ENERGY_MIN2SSD

parameters.name: FPDI
parameters.description: Unidirectional, differential flux vs energy (Isotropic assumption)

parameters.name: FPDI_RMSE
parameters.description: RMS error in ln(FPDI) including Poisson and Crosscal Errors

parameters.name: FPDI_Quality
parameters.description: Quality flag for FPDI fluxes: 0 - highest quality, 1 - problem with time resolution, 2 - contamination, 3 - saturation, 4 - other problem, 5 - possible electron background, 10 -not yet quality checked

parameters.name: DOSE1
parameters.description: Mission-Accumulated Dose in Dosimeter 1 (front)

parameters.name: DOSE1_RATE
parameters.description: Dose rate in Dosimeter 1 (front)

parameters.name: DOSE2
parameters.description: Mission-Accumulated Dose in Dosimeter 2 (side)

parameters.name: DOSE2_RATE
parameters.description: Dose rate in Dosimeter 2 (side)

parameters.name: L
parameters.description: McIlwain L of locally mirroring particle in OPQ

parameters.name: L_star
parameters.description: Roederer L of particle with 90 degree pitch angle in OPQ

parameters.name: Phi
parameters.description: Third (drift) invariant  of particle with 90 degree pitch angle in OPQ

parameters.name: Alpha_Eq
parameters.description: Equatorial pitch angle of particle with 90 degree pitch angle in OPQ

parameters.name: B_Calc
parameters.description: OPQ model magnetic field vector in GEO

parameters.name: B_Eq
parameters.description: OPQ model magnetic field strength at local minimum along local field line

parameters.name: MLT
parameters.description: Magnetic local time (OPQ)
